    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage, babied it every single weekend, and there\u2019s not a single scratch or dent to be found. It even still has that fresh new-car smell! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This specimen is mechanically superlative, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and a recently calibrated valve lash adjustment. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero panel gap irregularities, while the underside remains free of oxidation. This is a turn-key collector piece with a meticulously documented service history, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. Flawless paint and interior. Garage kept. Full service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
